<L>__{exterior forster camp dawn}
<A>__{med. shot angled through willows. a bearded man, cal forster, and two young fellows in their late teens squat beside a campfire eating breakfast. o.s. there is the sound of movement. lednov moves cautiously into the scene. he has a revolver in his hand. forster turns toward camera and fear comes into his expression. lednov fires. forster crumples near the fire. the two boys jump to their feet and reach for rifles. lednov fires again and again. mccall and peters come into the scene, both firing revolvers.}
